snippet.title: Data Council
snippet.description:
Data Council connects software engineers and data scientists around common challenges using open source data technologies. Our content and events are designed to give data professionals the knowledge and insights to build scalable, analytical systems to handle ever-increasing amounts of data. 

We bring you the best data-oriented tech talks from the top engineers from top technology companies and startups across the world. Subscribe to our YT channel to keep up with us!
